    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/f1919f62ee56c32e56f4e7f59057f430.poster.avif?t=1727470306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/f1919f62ee56c32e56f4e7f59057f430.webm?t=1727470306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/f1919f62ee56c32e56f4e7f59057f430.mp4?t=1727470306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《孤独监狱》是一款设定在空旷监狱中的心理恐怖游戏。在这个地方开始发生一些奇怪的事情，包括一些人失踪。在试图进一步调查时，当局下令将所有囚犯转移，但你贿赂了一名警卫留了下来，想利用这个机会逃离监狱。但这并不容易。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/f6643d19629cb523e719e3e408b0673c.poster.avif?t=1727470306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/f6643d19629cb523e719e3e408b0673c.webm?t=1727470306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/f6643d19629cb523e719e3e408b0673c.mp4?t=1727470306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《孤独监狱》专注于在紧张的环境中进行探索。你必须找到进入通常无法进入的地方的方法，解决谜题以解锁新区域，找到遗留的钥匙，同时悬疑和紧张的气氛将始终笼罩着你。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/fee33d09005ae602ea77f51dabca2b2a.poster.avif?t=1727470306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/fee33d09005ae602ea77f51dabca2b2a.webm?t=1727470306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087680/extras/fee33d09005ae602ea77f51dabca2b2a.mp4?t=1727470306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏不包含突然惊吓的场面！但这并不意味着你在游戏过程中不会感到害怕或被某些东西吓到，一切都是为了让你感到恐惧和紧张而设计的。<br><br><br>平均游戏时间：40分钟",
